[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "mr Pardon, as Olive observed, was a little out of this combination; but he was not a person to allow himself to droop.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "On her telling him that she never followed anything of that sort, he undertook a defence of the serial system, which she presently reminded him that she had not attacked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He was not discouraged by this retort, but glided gracefully off to the question of Mount Desert; conversation on some subject or other being evidently a necessity of his nature.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "His friends knew that in spite of his delicacy and his prattle he was what they called a live man; his appearance was perfectly reconcilable with a large degree of literary enterprise.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "For this ingenuous son of his age all distinction between the person and the artist had ceased to exist; the writer was personal, the person food for newsboys, and everything and every one were every one's business.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Since then he had ascended other steps of the same ladder; he was the most brilliant young interviewer on the Boston press.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He regarded the mission of mankind upon earth as a perpetual evolution of telegrams; everything to him was very much the same, he had no sense of proportion or quality; but the newest thing was what came nearest exciting in his mind the sentiment of respect.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000001_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000001_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Matthias had a mean opinion of Tarrant, thought him quite second rate, a votary of played out causes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He talked some time to Olive about Mount Desert, told her that in his letters he had described the company at the different hotels.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He remarked, however, that a correspondent suffered a good deal to day from the competition of the \"lady writers\"; the sort of article they produced was sometimes more acceptable to the papers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He supposed she would be glad to hear that-he knew she was so interested in woman's having a free field.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "They certainly made lovely correspondents; they picked up something bright before you could turn round; there wasn't much you could keep away from them; you had to be lively if you wanted to get there first.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Of course, they were naturally more chatty, and that was the style of literature that seemed to take most to day; only they didn't write much but what ladies would want to read.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "If you read a lady's letter you knew pretty well in advance what you would find.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Now, what he tried for was that you shouldn't have the least idea; he always tried to have something that would make you jump.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "mr Pardon was not conceited more, at least, than is proper when youth and success go hand in hand, and it was natural he should not know in what spirit Miss Chancellor listened to him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000002_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000002_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "The age seemed to her relaxed and demoralised, and I believe she looked to the influx of the great feminine element to make it feel and speak more sharply.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "It isn't often we have anything so fresh; it makes me feel as if I wanted to join in.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "First I catch one thing and then another; it seems as if I couldn't take it all in.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Perhaps I ought to pay more attention to mr Burrage; I don't want him to think we are not so cordial as they are in New York.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He thought there was too much hanging back; he wanted to see her in a front seat; he wanted to see her name in the biggest kind of bills and her portrait in the windows of the stores.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "She had charm, and there was a great demand for that nowadays in connexion with new ideas.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "There was a want of bold action; he didn't see what they were waiting for.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "mr Pardon went so far as to say that if dr Tarrant didn't see his way to do something, he should feel as if he should want to take hold himself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He knew that was a charge that people brought against newspaper men-that they were rather apt to cross the line.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He only worried because he thought those who were no doubt nearer to Miss Verena than he could hope to be were not sufficiently alive.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000021",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000021.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "She asked him, with a certain lofty coldness-he didn't make her shy, now, a bit-whether he took a great interest in the improvement of the position of women.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000004_000023",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000004_000023.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He was used to quick operations, however, and he had only a moment of bright blankness before replying:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"Oh, there is nothing I wouldn't do for the ladies; just give me a chance and you'll see.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Olive was silent a moment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"Well, sympathy is just sympathy-that's all I can say.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "It takes in Miss Verena and it takes in all others-except the lady correspondents,\" the young man added, with a jocosity which, as he perceived even at the moment, was lost on Verena's friend.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "He was not more successful when he went on: \"It takes in even you, Miss Chancellor!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "This young lady's worst apprehensions were now justified by mrs Tarrant's crying to her that she must not go, as mr Burrage and mr Gracie were trying to persuade Verena to give them a little specimen of inspirational speaking, and she was sure her daughter would comply in a moment if Miss Chancellor would just tell her to compose herself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"mr Burrage listens even better than he talks,\" his companion declared. \"We have the habit of attention at lectures, you know.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "To be lectured by you would be an advantage indeed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "We are sunk in ignorance and prejudice.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000014_000000",
