        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Selah had reappeared by this time; his lofty, contemplative person was framed by the doorway.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"Want to try a little inspiration?\" he inquired, looking round on the circle with an encouraging inflexion.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"You don't mean to say you ain't going to be supported?\" mrs Tarrant exclaimed, with dismay.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"Ah, I beseech you, give us the whole programme-don't omit any leading feature!\" mr Burrage was heard to plead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "I have no desire to draw attention to my own poor gifts.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "This declaration appeared to be addressed to Miss Chancellor.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"It will seem to come right down from-well, wherever it does come from.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Such chances were agitating; moreover, she didn't like, on any occasion, to be so prominent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "But everything that had been said was benighted and vulgar; the place seemed thick with the very atmosphere out of which she wished to lift Verena.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "They were treating her as a show, as a social resource, and the two young men from the College were laughing at her shamelessly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"I want you to address audiences that are worth addressing-to convince people who are serious and sincere.\" Olive herself, as she spoke, heard the great shake in her voice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"Your mission is not to exhibit yourself as a pastime for individuals, but to touch the heart of communities, of nations.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"Dear madam, I'm sure Miss Tarrant will touch my heart!\" mr Burrage objected, gallantly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Verena, diverted a moment from her communion with her friend, considered mr Burrage with a smile.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"You have no idea how much the way you say that increases my desire to hear you speak.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"Do as you please, my dear,\" said Olive, almost inaudibly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"I can see you don't want it,\" said Verena, wondering.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"You would stay if you liked it, wouldn't you?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "\"I don't know what I should do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "Come out with me!\" Olive spoke almost with fierceness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "mr Gracie seemed inclined to make the sturdiest protest.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "I suppose you'll think we go a good deal by what you say in this house.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000037_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000037_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "There's a little hole right there in the porch; it seems as if Doctor Tarrant couldn't remember to go for the man to fix it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000037_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000037_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "I can't stand a sleigh myself; it makes me sick.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "This was her hostess's response to Miss Chancellor's very summary farewell, uttered as the three ladies proceeded together to the door of the house.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000038_000001",
