        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "When the two young men from the College pressed their petition, she asked, with a laugh that surprised them, whether they wished to \"mock and muddle\" her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6353_63255_000062_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6353/63255/6353_63255_000062_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6353",
        "content": "But she didn't wish to marry him, all the same, and after he had gone she reflected that, once she came to think of it, she didn't want to marry any one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
